		{"id":"9d8013de056d9db5","type":"text","text":"通用按键统一显示在viewport 左下角\n使用键鼠时可点击，同时也可作为按键提示","x":1292,"y":-736,"width":408,"height":150},
		{"id":"effb336d07dd00cf","type":"file","file":"fd_prototype_docs/design/_assets/Pasted image 20260301145601.png","x":1296,"y":-539,"width":400,"height":232},
		{"id":"e44941d1773019a0","type":"file","file":"fd_prototype_docs/design/_assets/Pasted image 20260301150437.png","x":1296,"y":-287,"width":151,"height":57},
		{"id":"fa72675c90bc0434","type":"text","text":"统一按键规则\n\n- 手柄 A确认 B取消\n- 键鼠 左键点击确认/esc取消","x":934,"y":-736,"width":292,"height":150},
