		{"id":"781e518fbfc58310","type":"text","text":"按钮style： 圆角矩形/单色/无渐变/无半透明/按钮投影","x":1474,"y":28,"width":308,"height":60},
		{"id":"bdaf05249fab9d0b","type":"text","text":"为以后移植UE方便，需要能适配ue common ui的规范，可以导出按键的JSON  https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/common-ui-quickstart-guide-for-unreal-engine\n\n支持键鼠/手柄输入\n- 检测 latest input device， 并切换UI上按钮对应的按键提示","x":96,"y":-678,"width":498,"height":279},
